  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Blanch broccoli in boiling water for about 3 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and drain, then let it cool slightly.",
    "In a pan over medium-high heat, add olive oil and minced garlic. Sauté until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add blanched broccoli to the pan and toss with dark soft brown sugar. Stir well to coat.",
